================================================================================================================
PURPOSE OF THIS README

This file gives the infomation about the bug in the original implementation of cannon algorimthm provided in assignment 3
=================================================================================================================


=================================================================================================================
HOW TO EXPOSE THE BUG

The input files for cannon algorithm provided in this directory expose the bug in the original implementation
provided along with the 3rd assignment. 

The bug can be exposed by using the following combinations of input file provided. 

1. mpiexc -n 4 ./cannon 2x4.dat 4x2.dat [test]
2. mpiexc -n 4 ./cannon 4x4-1.dat 4x4-2.dat [test]
3. mpiexc -n 9 ./cannon 3x3-1.dat 3x3-2.dat [test]
4. mpiexc -n 9 ./cannon 3x3-1.dat 3x6.dat [test]
=================================================================================================================


